The paper discusses the challenges and methods for mining spatio-temporal data, which involves both spatial and temporal attributes. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
